  ** interface to 32-bit integer MPI enabled **

DIRAC master    (relativisticboost) starts by allocating       64000000 r*8 words (   0.477 GB) of memory
DIRAC nodes 1 to 15 starts by allocating            64000000 r*8 words (   0.477 GB) of memory
DIRAC master    (relativisticboost) to allocate at most      2147483648 r*8 words (  16.000 GB) of memory
DIRAC nodes 1 to 15 to allocate at most           2147483648 r*8 words (  16.000 GB) of memory
 
Note: maximum allocatable memory for master+nodes can be set by -aw (MW)/-ag (GB) flags in pam
 
